pageProduct.name: Pregnosis In Stream 1 Test
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Pregnosis In-Stream Early Detection 1 Test

From the beginning of pregnancy, the body produces hCG (Human Chorionic Gonadotropin) which is present in the urine. The level of this hormone increases as the pregnancy progresses. Pregnosis is easy to use and accurately detects levels of hCG as low as 10IU/L in urine. Pregnosis can be used to test up to 6 days before your missed period.

Size: 1 Test

KEY FEATURES

• • Simple and easy to use
• • Results can be seen in as little as 3 minutes
• • Accurately detects levels of hCG as low as 10IU/L in urine
• • Can be used as early as 6 days before your missed period
• • Australian owned

Warnings

The carton is security sealed. Do not purchase if the seal is broken. Each test is individually foil wrapped for the consumer's protection

Directions

Hold the Pregnosis in-stream test in the urine stream for at least 10 seconds until it is thoroughly wet and read the results after 3 minutes have passed. Two lines indicate a positive result. One line indicates a negative result. Do not read the result after 10 minutes; disregard any result lines or 'shadow' lines that appear after 10 minutes.

STORAGE AND DISPOSAL

Store below 25°C in a dry place. Do not freeze.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a dry place. Do not freeze.
